\begin{abstract}
It is shown that the kernel of
the
Fock representation of
a certain
Wick algebra
with braided operator of coefficients $T$, $||T\,||\le 1$, coincides
with the largest quadratic Wick ideal. Improved conditions on the
operator $T$ for the Fock inner product to be strictly positive
are given.
\end{abstract}

